<h2>Hi <%= @customer.name %>,</h2>

<p>We wanted to let you know that the status of your support ticket has changed.</p>

<table style="border-collapse: collapse;">
  <tr>
    <td style="padding: 6px;"><strong>Title:</strong></td>
    <td style="padding: 6px;"><%= @ticket.subject %></td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td style="padding: 6px;"><strong>Current Status:</strong></td>
    <td style="padding: 6px;"><%= @ticket.status.humanize %></td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td style="padding: 6px;"><strong>Description:</strong></td>
    <td style="padding: 6px;"><%= @ticket.description %></td>
  </tr>
</table>

<p>If you have any questions, feel free to reply to this email or log into your account for more details.</p>

<p>Thank you,<br>Support Team</p>
